data.description: The backyard has mature trees backing up to the waterway giving Extra privacy, 16x12 Pergola, 20x20 workshop. Partially Updated & remodeled and opened kitchen/dining room. Large living area with fireplace and opens up to the Florida room about 200 square feet(definite BONUS) with lots of windows to the backyard.  Master bathroom has been updated/remodeled with an amazing Tandem Shower.  Many can lights throughout.  Extra wide driveway with a RV electrical plug hookup.  Roof is about 1 1/2 years old.
